                    <span>A must for everyone dealing with Unix backup and recovery, HA stuff.<P>Many thanks to the author.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">This author can feel your pain!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>0</span>
