                    <span>Even though I was still very new to Linux/UNIX, this book was able to help me create a fully automated backup routine as well as how to restore from those backups. I found the book very easy to read and not at all dry.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A Must-have!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
